flavorText: NSLOCTEXT("", "5219B36A4C6AC903703D5088EB9A24E2", "I found a scholar\'s journal entry that indicates he is in search of a goblin rune in the Aela Ruins. If I can locate the rune first and then locate the scholar, a reward might be coming my way. ")
